And in the Kostroma and Magadan regions, the concept of “social entrepreneurship” and the directions of support of social entrepreneurship are being strengthened in the normative and legal field.
All proposals from the regions will be taken into account in the preparation of state programmes to support small and medium-sized enterprises, and the most important will be developed in the form of specific bills.
